---
const includes = [
  'Personal advisor relationship throughout your membership',
  'Carefully curated introductions, one at a time',
  'You are consulted before every introduction',
  'Ongoing support and guidance from your advisor',
  'Full discretion and POPIA-compliant privacy protection',
  'No automatic renewal — entirely your decision',
];
---

<div class="membership-card">
  <div class="membership-badge">
    <span class="badge badge-gold">Membership by Invitation Only</span>
  </div>

  <div class="membership-name">
    <span class="eyebrow">Executive Membership</span>
    <div class="membership-price">
      <span class="price-amount">R2,500</span>
      <span class="price-period">once-off · 6 months</span>
    </div>
    <span class="gold-rule" role="presentation"></span>
  </div>

  <ul class="membership-includes" role="list">
    {includes.map(item => (
      <li>
        <span class="check-icon" aria-hidden="true">◆</span>
        <span>{item}</span>
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>

  <div class="membership-note">
    <p>The membership fee is discussed openly during your coffee meeting. There are no hidden fees and no automatic renewals.</p>
  </div>

  <a href="/enquire" class="btn btn-primary membership-cta">Begin Your Enquiry</a>
</div>

<style>
.membership-card {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--color-gold-light);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--space-2xl);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-gold);
  max-width: 560px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.membership-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-gold), var(--color-turq));
}

.membership-badge {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.membership-name {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.membership-price {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin: 0.5rem 0 var(--space-sm);
}

.price-amount {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1;
}

.price-period {
  font-family: var(--font-accent);
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  font-style: italic;
}

.membership-includes {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}

.membership-includes li {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
  font-size: var(--text-base);
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.55;
}

.check-icon {
  color: var(--color-gold);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 0.45rem;
}

.membership-note {
  background: var(--color-gold-tint);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.membership-note p {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  margin: 0;
  max-width: none;
}

.membership-cta {
  width: 100%;
  text-align: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
</style>
